Introduction

This is a quick output of WT and L-Bmal-KO SPF and GF mice RCF outputs taken from commit 01bdffb.

source("load_data.R")
chan <- c("VO2", "RQ", "kcal")

SPF before wheel

cond <- "SPF"
cond2 <- "MR"
data <- list("Total"=total[[cond]][[cond2]], "Light"=light[[cond]][[cond2]], "Dark"=dark[[cond]][[cond2]])
lapply(chan, function(x) analysis(x, data, channels, cond, graphs = TRUE, verbose = F, retur = FALSE, cuts = 50))
